data.name: Label9.Text
data.value: Enchanted Bloom simplifies the process of sending thoughtful gifts to the remarkable men in your life! Explore our exquisite collection of gifts curated exclusively for men and seize the opportunity to surprise them today, all with the convenience of same-day delivery throughout the Philippines!

data.name: description.Text
data.value: What’s a healthy, yummy gift you can send? Fruit baskets! At Flower Chimp, our fruit baskets come in a variety of sizes. Large fruit baskets are great as you can fit a whole lots of goodies in them. Send large fruit baskets to your loved ones anywhere in the Philippines.
